trailingComments.value:
*
 * Controls a dropdown type of input
 *
 * #### SCSS import:
 * ```
 * @import "~@orloxx/ui-core/scss/form/dropdown-field";
 * ```
 *
 * @extends {Field}
 *
 * @example
 * <DropdownField id='sex' name='sex' label='Sex'>
 *   <option value='M'>Male</option>
 *   <option value='F'>Female</option>
 * </DropdownField>
